     A*================================================================
     A* POKEBATTL - Pokemon Battle Display File
     A* 27x132 for Mocha 5250
     A*
     A* Color indicators (set by POKEBATTLE before WRITE):
     A*   Player side (PLART*):  30=GRN 31=WHT 32=RED 33=TRQ 34=YLW 35=PNK 36=BLU
     A*   Opponent side (OPART*): 40=GRN 41=WHT 42=RED 43=TRQ 44=YLW 45=PNK 46=BLU
     A*   Only one indicator per side should be on at a time.
     A*================================================================
     A                                      DSPSIZ(27 132)
     A                                      CA03(03 'F3=Exit')
     A*
     A*== HEADER - Row 1 (written first, clears screen) ===========
     A          R HEADER
     A                                  1  2'P O K E 4 0 0   B A T T L E'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A            ROOMCD         8A  O  1 55
     A            BMODE          2A  O  1 65
     A*
     A*== OPPONENT - Rows 2-12 ====================================
     A*  Info on LEFT, art on RIGHT (Gen 1 layout: enemy faces you)
     A          R OPPONENT
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                      PUTOVR
     A                                      CLRL(*NO)
     A                                      FRCDTA
     A                                  2  5'Enemy:'
     A            OPNAME        12A  O  2 12
     A                                      OVRDTA
